ATTRIBUTION REQUIREMENTS
========================

If you use, modify, or distribute this software or any derivative works, you MUST:

1. Give appropriate credit:
   - Include the text: "Based on Thoughts & Time by Sawt Dakhili"
   - Provide a link to the original project: https://github.com/sawtdakhili/Thoughts-Time
   - Provide a link to the license: https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/

2. Indicate if changes were made:
   - State what modifications you have made to the original work
   - Example: "Modified to add feature X" or "Customized UI for organization Y"

3. ShareAlike requirement:
   - Any derivative works must be distributed under the same CC BY-NC-SA 4.0 license
   - You cannot relicense derivatives under a more restrictive or permissive license

4. NonCommercial restriction:
   - You may NOT use this software for commercial purposes
   - Commercial use includes: selling the software, using it in a commercial product or service, or using it in a business context for profit
   - If you wish to use this commercially, contact the copyright holder for a separate license

RECOMMENDED ATTRIBUTION FORMAT
==============================

For source code:
```
// Based on Thoughts & Time by Sawt Dakhili
// https://github.com/sawtdakhili/Thoughts-Time
// Licensed under CC BY-NC-SA 4.0
// Modified: [describe your changes]
```

For documentation/README:
```
This project is based on [Thoughts & Time](https://github.com/sawtdakhili/Thoughts-Time)
by Sawt Dakhili, licensed under [CC BY-NC-SA 4.0](https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/).

Changes made: [describe your modifications]
```

For UI/About page:
```
Based on Thoughts & Time by Sawt Dakhili
https://github.com/sawtdakhili/Thoughts-Time
```

